<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆参加了皇家活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看。”厨师说，“抽签游戏！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抽签游戏很有意思的。”皇家织工说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们玩儿一下吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都在袋子里放了一张礼物卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨师放了一张免费吃饭的卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>理发师提供了一次免费理发的卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆的卡上写着：一次免费的魔法咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都抽出了一张卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轮到汤姆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出了一张卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抽到了皇家织工的小地毯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来轮到德克了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆很紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克很不好相处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆不希望为他施魔法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克抽出了一张卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看，皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你拿到了什么？”厨师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克什么都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果德克抽到我的卡怎么办？”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人也都去抽了卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，只剩了一张卡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个骑士把手伸进了袋子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊！”骑士说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抽到了魔法咒语卡！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吓坏我了！”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很高兴德克没有抽到他的卡片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来那个骑士走到了汤姆面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明天去实验室找你。”骑士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆害怕得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士的表情令人觉得非常不舒服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>